<form name="CoachRosterNotice" startPoint="false" themePath="mvsc" dataEntryOnly="true" process="Post-CoachRosterNotice">
<items>
<heading label="H1" type="Sub"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="360" color="000000">Coach's Team and Roster Notification</font></paragraph></heading>
<text label="T1"><table indent="0"><row><cell width="3645"><division indent="0" align="left"><font color="0066CC"><u><invitation form="Preseason" project="">Back to Preseason Setup</invitation></u></font></division></cell><cell width="3600"><division indent="0" align="left"><font color="0066CC"><u><invitation form="AdminDash" project="">Back to Administrator Dashboard</invitation></u></font></division></cell></row></table></text>
<text label="T2" style="instructional"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>This tool permits you to send a personal email to one or more coaches with his team assignment and Dashboard link.  On his Dashboard, he will find detailed information about his team roster, including contact information for all of the players.</font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>You may also pass along whatever other information you choose (such as, for example, a link to the season schedule Web page)</font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>Fill in the blanks below.  The parts of the letter that are composed by the Tawala program are inserted so you can see how the overall letter will read.</font></paragraph></text>
<text label="T3" style="instructional"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>Note: If you want to communicate with a coach or coaches without sending out the "Coach Notification" below, use the </font><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="Communicator" project="">Communicator</invitation></u></font><font> on your Dashboard.</font></paragraph></text>
<fib label="Q1" style="topLabels"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">From </font><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000"><i>(name): </i></font><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000"> </font><blank label="a" length="57" required="false" alternateLabel="FromAdminName"/></paragraph></fib>
<fib label="Q2" style="topLabels"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">From </font><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000"><i>(Email): </i></font><sp/><blank label="a" length="57" required="false" alternateLabel="FromEmail"/></paragraph></fib>
<fib label="Q3" style="topLabels"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Subject:  </font><blank label="a" length="57" required="false" alternateLabel="Subject"/></paragraph></fib>
<mc label="Q4" onlyone="true" required="false"><question><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">To:</font></paragraph></question><choice label="a"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">All coaches</font></paragraph></choice><choice label="b"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Only the coaches I select below</font></paragraph></choice></mc>
<text label="T4"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>Dear &lt;First Name of Coach&gt;,</font></paragraph></text>
<fib label="Q5" style="topLabels"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Enter the first part of your message: </font><blank label="a" length="57" height="10" required="false" alternateLabel="Body"/></paragraph></fib>
<text label="T5"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>You will be the coach for &lt;TeamName&gt; in this season's </font><font><field name="League"/></font><font> League.</font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>You can find important contact information for your team and the League on your personal </font><font color="0000FF"><u>Coach Dashboard</u></font><font>.  The Dashboard will also permit you to communicate easily with your team members and keep track of various responsibilities during the season.</font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font><field name="DashboardLinkVerbiage2"/></font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>Once again, in order to gain access to your coaching tools for this season's </font><font><field name="League"/></font><font>, click on this link:</font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font color="0000FF"><u>Coach Dashboard</u></font></paragraph></text>
<fib label="Q6" style="topLabels"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Enter the closing of your message, including your signoff </font><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000"><i>(e.g. Yours,  Kerry)</i></font><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">: </font><blank label="a" length="57" height="5" required="false" alternateLabel="Close"/></paragraph></fib>
<skipInstructions>
<if>
<conditions>
<mcEquals field="CoachRosterNotice:Q4" value="a"/>
</conditions>
<trueSet>
<skip to="T7"/>
</trueSet>
</if>
</skipInstructions>
<text label="T6"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><table indent="0"><row><cell width="3600"><division indent="0" align="left"><font color="0066CC"><u><invitation form="Preseason" project="">Back to Preseason Setup</invitation></u></font></division></cell><cell width="3600"><division indent="0" align="left"><font color="0066CC"><u><invitation form="AdminDash" project="">Back to Administrator Dashboard</invitation></u></font></division></cell></row></table></text>
<mc label="Q7" onlyone="false" required="false"><question><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Select the coach or coaches you wish to send this message to:</font></paragraph></question><data-provider><dynamic-mcq version="1"><display-expression><field name="Record:Coach:FullName"/>
<string value=" ("/>
<field name="Record:Coach:Team"/>
<string value=")"/>
</display-expression><value-expression><field name="Record:Coach:CoachId"/>
</value-expression><sort-expression><field name="Record:Coach:LastName"/>
</sort-expression><record-selector><form name="Coach" /></record-selector></dynamic-mcq></data-provider></mc>
<break/>
<text label="T7"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><table indent="0"><row><cell width="3600"><division indent="0" align="left"><font color="0066CC"><u><invitation form="Preseason" project="">Back to Preseason Setup</invitation></u></font></division></cell><cell width="3600"><division indent="0" align="left"><font color="0066CC"><u><invitation form="AdminDash" project="">Back to Administrator Dashboard</invitation></u></font></division></cell></row></table></text>
<text label="T8" style="instructional"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><table indent="540"><row><cell width="10260"><division indent="0" align="left"><font><b>To: </b></font><font>&lt;Coach's Name&gt;</font></division></cell></row><row><cell width="10260"><division indent="0" align="left"><font><b>From: </b></font><font><field name="CoachRosterNotice:FromAdminName"/></font><font> (</font><font><field name="CoachRosterNotice:FromEmail"/></font><font>)</font></division></cell></row><row><cell width="10260"><division indent="0" align="left"><font><b>Date:</b></font><font> Today</font></division></cell></row><row><cell width="10260"><division indent="0" align="left"><sp/><sp/></division></cell></row><row><cell width="10260"><division indent="0" align="left"><font><b>Subject:</b></font><sp/><font><field name="CoachRosterNotice:Subject"/></font></division></cell></row><row><cell width="10260"><division indent="0" align="left"><sp/></division></cell></row><row><cell width="10260"><division indent="0" align="left"><font>Dear &lt;Coach's First Name&gt;,</font></division></cell></row><row><cell width="10260"><division indent="0" align="left"><sp/><sp/><sp/></division></cell></row><row><cell width="10260"><division indent="0" align="left"><font><field name="CoachRosterNotice:Body"/></font></division></cell></row><row><cell width="10260"><division indent="0" align="left"><sp/><sp/><sp/></division></cell></row><row><cell width="10260"><division indent="0" align="left"><font>You will be the coach for &lt;TeamName&gt; in this season's </font><font><field name="League"/></font><font> League.</font></division><division indent="0" align="left"><sp/></division><division indent="0" align="left"><font>You can find important contact information for your team and the League on your personal </font><font color="0000FF"><u>Coach Dashboard</u></font><font>.  The Dashboard will also permit you to communicate easily with your team members and keep track of various responsibilities during the season.</font></division><division indent="0" align="left"><sp/></division><division indent="0" align="left"><font><field name="DashboardLinkVerbiage2"/></font></division><division indent="0" align="left"><sp/></division><division indent="0" align="left"><font>Once again, in order to gain access to your coaching tools for this season's </font><font><field name="League"/></font><font>, click on this link:</font></division><division indent="720" align="left"><sp/></division><division indent="720" align="left"><font color="0000FF"><u>Coach Dashboard</u></font></division></cell></row><row><cell width="10260"><division indent="0" align="left"><sp/><sp/></division></cell></row><row><cell width="10260"><division indent="0" align="left"><font><field name="CoachRosterNotice:Close"/></font></division></cell></row></table></text>
<mc label="Q8" onlyone="true" required="false"><question><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Select:</font></paragraph></question><choice label="a"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Send the email out</font></paragraph></choice><choice label="b"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Edit the email</font></paragraph></choice><choice label="c"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Abandon the email and return to Administrator Dashboard</font></paragraph></choice></mc>
<text label="T9" style="instructional"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>It might take several minutes to send all the emails. Please wait for the next page to appear. Do not click "Submit" again! </font></paragraph></text>
</items>
</form>
<form name="ShowTeamRosters" startPoint="false" themePath="mvsc" process="Post-ShowTeamRosters">
<items>
<heading label="H1" type="Sub"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="360" color="000000">Team Rosters</font></paragraph></heading>
<text label="T1"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><table indent="0"><row><cell width="5400"><division indent="0" align="left"><font color="0066CC"><u><invitation form="AdminDash" project="">Back to Administrator Dashboard</invitation></u></font></division></cell><cell width="5400"><division indent="0" align="left"><font color="0066CC"><u><invitation form="Team Rosters" project="">Assign Players to Teams</invitation></u></font></division></cell></row></table></text>
<mc label="Q1" onlyone="true" required="false"><question><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph></question><choice label="a"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Display all rosters, one at a time, on separate pages</font></paragraph></choice><choice label="b"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Display only one roster</font></paragraph></choice></mc>
<skipInstructions>
<if>
<conditions>
<mcEquals field="ShowTeamRosters:Q1" value="a"/>
</conditions>
<trueSet>
<skip to="__EndOfForm__"/>
</trueSet>
</if>
</skipInstructions>
<mc label="Q2" alternateLabel="TeamId" onlyone="true" required="false"><question><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Select a team roster to view </font></paragraph></question><data-provider><dynamic-mcq version="1"><display-expression><field name="Record:Team:TeamId"/>
</display-expression><value-expression><field name="Record:Team:TeamId"/>
</value-expression><sort-expression></sort-expression><record-selector><form name="Team" /></record-selector></dynamic-mcq></data-provider></mc>
<break/>
<text label="T2"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><table indent="0"><row><cell width="5400"><division indent="0" align="left"><font color="0066CC"><u><invitation form="AdminDash" project="">Back to Administrator Dashboard</invitation></u></font></division></cell><cell width="5400"><division indent="0" align="left"><font color="0066CC"><u><invitation form="Team Rosters" project="">Assign Players to Teams</invitation></u></font></division></cell></row></table></text>
<text label="T3"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="720"/><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font><itemization-table version="2"><number-of-columns>6</number-of-columns><column><header><string value="Team"/>
</header><contents><field name="Record:Registration:TeamId" /></contents></column><column><header><string value="First"/>
</header><contents><field name="Record:Registration:FirstName" /></contents></column><column><header><string value="Last"/>
</header><contents><field name="Record:Registration:LastName" /></contents></column><column><header><string value="Parent"/>
</header><contents><field name="Record:Registration:ParentFirstName" /></contents></column><column><header><field name="Phone1Lab"/>
</header><contents><field name="Record:Registration:Phone1" /></contents></column><column><header><string value="Uniform Size"/>
</header><contents><field name="Record:Registration:UniformSize" /></contents></column><conditions><form name="Registration" /><conditions>
<mcEquals field="ShowTeamRosters:TeamId">
<string field="Record:Registration:TeamId"/>
</mcEquals>
</conditions></conditions></itemization-table></font></paragraph></text>
</items>
</form>
